NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: SOLDIER SNIPE, I READ THE NAUGHTY ASSOCIATE BEHAVIOURAL REPORT FORM... @IT SEEMS YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR DROPPING THAT SAW BLADE!
AN ACT OF SABOTAGE! YOU'RE A DIRTY TRAITOR!! I CAN SEE IT IN YOUR EYES!
NO!! IT WASN'T EVEN ME! THERE WAS A ROCK SLIDE...
SHUT IT, TRAITOR SNIPE!
TRAITORS AND FOOLS ALL AROUND ME!!! OHHH HOW I KNOW IT!
WELL SNIPE. @I MUST INFORM YOU THAT AS PER THE EMPLOYEE INCOMPETENCE CLAUSE 389...
WE MUST, REGRETTABLY, LET YOU GO.
SOLDIER... LET SNIPE GO.
NOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!!!
AHAHAHA. 'LET GO'. HAHAHA.
AM I NOT EXTREMELY SKILLED WITH PUNS AND WORDPLAY?
INDEED, OH MAGNIFICENT HUMGRUMP. ONE OF THE BEST.
THE BEST.
THE BEST. APOLOGIES, OH MASTERFUL ONE.
{200}NOW GET BACK TO WORK!!!
ALRIGHT! CLEAR ENOUGH, ASSOCIATES?! BACK TO WORK!! @WAIT...
TROUBLESOME PERSONS! TROUBLESOME PERSONS!
OBLITERATE THEM!!!
JOT...I'M A PRETTY CHILL DUDE BUT...
THESE CREEPS STRUTTING AROUND MY VILLAGE AS IF THEY OWN THE PLACE... @{150}IT'S REALLY GETTING MY GOAT!
I CAN FEEL THE TRARRG SPIRIT RISING IN ME...
IT'S TIME WE KICKED THESE MARAUDERS OFF THE MOUNTAIN! @TIME I STOOD UP AND JOINED YOU IN COMBAT...
{150}FOR TRARRG!!!
